One day the strongest person in the world disappeared. An old man who was suffering from dementia and couldnt remember himself appeared in front of the village boy So-Woon. So-Woon takes care of him carefully and later the old man teaches him martial arts. One day he finds that the old man whom he was taking care of and who taught him martial arts disappeared. So-Woon knew that the old man must have come to his senses and left him without saying anything. Six years later So-Woon becomes the symbol of Pungcheon. Together with his friends So-Guk-Ju and Pyo-Guk he started a long journey to become The Worlds Best Escort and to find his master and
